{"tid":1963023,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"烏甸尼斯總監：英超即將宣佈中止球季","createTime":"2020-04-08T00:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T10:48:30.000Z","uid":165817,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1cc0b948d953d2993242a4df7e4cb46414bd33","tid":1963023,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"意甲球會烏甸尼斯的體育總監馬連奴 (Pierpaolo Marino) 透露：「英超即將宣佈中止球季。」<br />\n<br />\n烏甸尼斯與英格蘭的屈福特都是普素家族旗下的球會，前者由父親基岩柏奧路普素 (Giampaolo Pozzo) 所擁有，而兒子真奴普素 (Gino Pozzo) 則持有屈福特。<br />\n<br />\n馬連奴表示：「比利時足總已經中止了聯賽。在英格蘭，英超也即將發佈類似的聲明，因為那裏的情況正在變得非常、非常嚴重。」<br />\n<br />\n「坦白說，我只希望我們能夠在疫情過後再次享受足球。不管需要多長時間，我們都要走出這個危險地帶。」<br />\n<br />\n「我擔心的是下個球季，而不是今個。」"},{"pid":"f8ab370856854a51e941f996d7a10a4569d45c8d","tid":1963023,"uid":67225,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"「我擔心的是下個球季，而不是今個。」<br />\n<br />\n開唔到下季真係死得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6625e98e19a4f2ca923faa2635b16c8431996b8","tid":1963023,"uid":29916,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:01:45.000Z","msg":"意粉成日反利 真世仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af433ced8cbd2421d68c8e753218140a087eca0f","tid":1963023,"uid":236422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"平常心"},{"pid":"573d2856abba1fccc85cc3d91843690914f96cc3","tid":1963023,"uid":197474,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"類似比利士 = 直接頒冠軍<br />\n利狗有運行"},{"pid":"8e00990a41ff4690b68b20a8d549fda6dabb80b3","tid":1963023,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://global.espn.com/football/liverpool-engliverpool/story/4083275/liverpool-will-win-premier-league-despite-coronavirus-uefa-president-ceferin\" data-sr-url=\"https://